with it." This fork is distributed under GPLv3 per the terms above.

Third-party components used by Ramblr and their licenses:

- sherpa-onnx (https://github.com/k2-fsa/sherpa-onnx) — Apache License 2.0
  Used for on-device speech transcription. Native libraries are downloaded
  at build time (see app/build.gradle.kts), not vendored in this repo.

- llama.cpp (https://github.com/ggml-org/llama.cpp) — MIT License
  Used for on-device cleanup/post-processing. Included as a git submodule
  (see .gitmodules); not modified beyond the JNI shim in
  app/src/main/cpp/llama_cleanup/.

- OkHttp (https://square.github.io/okhttp/) — Apache License 2.0
