  — Apache License 2.0

Cloud transcription and cleanup calls (OpenAI, Anthropic, Gemini, or an
optional self-hosted OpenAI-compatible endpoint you configure) are made
directly from the device using your own API key — no third-party SDKs
are vendored for these; see PRIVACY.md for the full data-flow description.
